@server_HostAddress = http://localhost:5053

GET {{server_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:5053/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5053/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Log a city view
POST {{server_HostAddress}}/api/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

{
  "city": "Vilnius",
  "timestamp": "2025-10-05T12:00:00Z",
  "temperatureC": 12.5,
  "feelsLikeC": 10.1,
  "conditions": "Cloudy"
}

### Get user history
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/log/history
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

### Get top viewed cities
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/log/top-cities?take=5
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

### Get hottest and coldest logged entries
GET {{server_HostAddress}}/api/log/extremes
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>